When the monster's health is less than half, it will enter an angry state and emit a golden light from its body. At this point, the monster will gain some powerful buffs. But if you can get it into the Weak State with black smoke, you can defeat it more easily.
Help Gunner to kill a Metal mutt.

Open your backpack and equip your sword and kill 5 Metal mutts.
Enter thetown and find Nash.

- Press [Esc] to open your talent tree interface 
- select upgrade main branch 
- select upgrade War Stomp skill 
- place the skill in the quick slot

Use a hoe to loosen the soil in the field, and then use seeds to sow on the loosened soil.
Plant 5 Bamboo Seeds, 5 Trifoliums Seeds, and 5 Carrots Seeds in field.

After planting the seeds, they need to be watered patiently three or four times before they mature. Once they are ready, you can approach it to harvest them. After that, go find Silas. He needs those.
Open the Gather Crafting and refine a Gather Essence. Before that, you need to obtain enough materials.

Get 5 Ordinary Wood.
Get 5 Stones.
Get 5 Ordinary Wood and 5 Fibers to make an Iron Pickaxe.

You have learned how to upgrade the talent tree and make equipment, try to gather some more advanced materials:
Get a Dark Iron Ore.
Get a Desert Tree.
Get an Ice Cap Mushroom.

Based on the latest intelligence:
Cactus Warriors - Has high defense, using heavy attacks can break through its defense.
Pumpkin Fiends - Possess remote skills, using Trampling can make it unable to use remote skills.

Try making a Stone Sword in Combat Crafting, stronger weapons can make you more relaxed in battle.
Before that, you need to unlock the recipe for Stone Sword in the talent tree.

You have learned how to upgrade the talent tree and make equipment, try to defeat stronger monsters:
Kill a Buzz Buddy.
Kill a Mine Cat.
Kill a Leafy Lurker.
Open your talent tree and switch to the farming tree. Upgrade your Capture skill node on the far right.
If you want your crops to grow faster, you need a more advanced hoe. Try to crafting an Iron Hoe.

You have learned how to upgrade the talent tree and make equipment, try to plant more advanced seeds:
Plant Cotton seeds.
Plant Pitcher Plant seeds.
Plant Endurance Fruit seeds.
Go to the exchange and buy something.
